name: v2026.01.1
body:
## What's Changed

- Updated [`epp-16-ns-data`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/v2026.01/rst-test-specs.html#Data-Provider-epp-16-ns-data) to ensure all error codes are included ([#19](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/19)).
- Updated [epp-23](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/v2026.01/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-23) to check that the EPP server rejects rename commands for external host objects that have associations with objects that are sponsored by a different client ([#89](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/89)).
- Updated the [`rdap.baseURLs`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/v2026.01/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-rdap.baseURLs) and [`srsgw.rdapBaseURLs`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/v2026.01/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-srsgw.rdapBaseURLs) input parameters to require a trailing slash ([#186](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/186)).
- Clarified that the `ICANNRST` repository ID MAY be used, not MUST ([#188](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/188)).
- Account for differing interpretations of idempotency in EPP in [epp-16](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/v2026.01/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-16) ([#190](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/190)).

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/compare/v2026.01...v2026.01.1

name: v2025.09
body:
## What's Changed

* The [Configuration Parameters](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#config) section has been updated to include the version of the RDAP Conformance Tool that is used ([#106](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/106)).

* [epp-03](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Case-epp-03) has been updated to confirm that the server rejects a <login> command with a valid client ID and password, but where the client has not provided a certificate ([#101](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/101)).

* The version of Zonemaster has been updated to 2024.2 (Zonemaster::Engine version 7.0.0) ([#125](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/152))

* [rdap-08](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Case-rdap-08), [rdap-09](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Case-rdap-09) and [rdap-10](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Case-rdap-10) have been added to the [RDAP Test Suite](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Suite-StandardRDAP) to verify correct behaviour of servers that receive queries for non-existent domain, nameserver or entity objects ([#76](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/76)).

* [epp-25](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Case-epp-25) has been added ([#73](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/73)).

* [srsgw-08](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/releases/new#Test-Case-srsgw-08) has been updated to correct an error where the spec erroneously expects that a <renew> command will remove the addPeriod RGP status (due to [Erratum 8305](https://www.rfc-editor.org/errata/eid8305)) ([#13](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/13)).

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/compare/v2025.08.1...v2025.09

name: v2025.08.1
body:
## What's Changed

This release updates the configuration file(s) for the RDAP Conformance Tool. There are no changes to the test specifications.

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/compare/v2025.08...v2025.08.1

### Note

Releases of the RST v2.0 test specifications do not always align with releases of the RST v2.0 service, as it is often necessary to publish an update to the test specs before the corresponding update to the test system.

As described in the [API spec](https://github.com/icann/rst-api-spec), the `testPlan` property of test objects includes the version of the test specs that is used for performing tests. This can be used to determine which version of the test specs is currently deployed in the given environment (OT&E or production).

name: v2025.08
body:
## What's Changed

* Updates to the EPP Extension Registry ([#94](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/94), ([#102](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/102) and [#133](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/133)).

* Added [`epp.supportedContactPostalInfoTypes`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-epp.supportedContactPostalInfoTypes) input parameter ([#96](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/96)).

* Added [`RPMS_MISSING_CLAIMS_KEY`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Error-RPMS_MISSING_CLAIMS_KEY) ([#18](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/18)).

* Removed the `integration.rriACL` input parameter ([#98](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/98)).

* [Configuration parameters](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#config) are now included in HTML output ([#108](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/108)).

* Minor fixes to [epp-02](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-02) and [epp-08](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-08) ([#110](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/110) and [#113](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/113)).

* [epp-04](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-04), [epp-05](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-05) and [epp-06](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-06) have been updated so that they will accept any EPP error response when submitting a `<check>` command for a syntactically invalid domain name, host name, or contact ID ([#115](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/115)).

* [epp-11](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-11) will no longer fail if the EPP server allows creation of internal hosts without glue ([#120](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/120)).

* Many SRS Gateway error codes have been downgraded from `CRITICAL` to `ERROR` severity ([#125](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/125)).

* Minor fixes to several RDAP test cases ([#129](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/129)).

* The build system will now generate separate RDAP Conformance Tool configuration files for the OT&E and production environments ([#131](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/131)).

* Updated [`idn.testLabelsForOTE`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Resource-idn.testLabelsForOTE) to the latest version.



**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/compare/v2025.07...v2025.08

name: v2025.07
body:
## What's Changed
- Account for out-of-band purge of the domain in [epp-21](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-21) and [srsgw-08](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-srsgw-08) ([#6](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/6))
- [epp-08](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-08): do not expect the 2201 code ([#54](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/54))
- [srsgw-08](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-srsgw-08): incorrect expected RGP status after `<delete>` ([#69](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/69))
- [rdap-92](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-rdap-92): ordering of objects in arrays ([#61](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/61))
- Add unique ID to data provider rows ([#87](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/87))
- [epp-16-dnssec-data](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Data-Provider-epp-16-dnssec-data): differentiate between secDNS interfaces ([#78](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/78))
- Server use of error result code for `<check>` for invalid domain/hostnames causes issues in [epp-04](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-04), [epp-05](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-05) and [epp-06](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-epp-06) ([#62](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/62))

- Update to the EPP Extension Registry ([#85](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/85))

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/compare/v2025.06...v2025.07

name: v2025.06
body:
- Added the [`RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_CRRR`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Error-RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_CRRR), [`RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_UPRR`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Error-RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_UPRR), [`RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_RERR`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Error-RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_RERR) and [`RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_ACRR`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Error-RDE_DOMAIN_HAS_INVALID_ACRR) error codes to [rde-07](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Test-Case-rde-07) (see #53).

- Added the [`epp.client01ChainCert`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Resource-epp.client01ChainCert) and [`epp.client02ChainCert`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Resource-epp.client02ChainCert) resources (see #63).

- The schema for the [`rdap.profileVersion`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-rdap.profileVersion) input parameter has been updated to reflect the retirement of the February-2019 profile (see #64).

- Fixed an issue with the script that generates the RDAP Conformance Tool configuration file.

- Ensure EPP-related resources are referenced by all suites that relate to EPP.

name: v2025.03
body:
Stable release v2025.03:

  - Describe the use of `.icann` for external nameserver hostnames ([#9](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/9))
  - Allow `v4Addrs` and `v6Addrs` to be optional in [`dnssecOps.nameservers`](#Input-Parameter-dnssecOps.nameservers)
    ([#11](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/11))
  - Clarify that the [`epp.supportedContactElements`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-epp.supportedContactElements) and [`epp.requiredContactElements`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-epp.requiredContactElements) input parameters **MUST** be empty if the value of the [`general.registryDataModel`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-general.registryDataModel) input parameter is `minimum`([#23](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/23))
  - Describe the use of `ICANNRST` as an EPP repository ID that may be used in RSP evaluation tests and OT&E ([#24](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/24))
  - Add a new `hostModel` column to [`epp-16-ns-data`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Data-Provider-epp-16-ns-data) ([#28](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/28))

name: v2025.02
body:
- Fix the example in [`dnssecOps.nameservers`](https://icann.github.io/rst-test-specs/rst-test-specs.html#Input-Parameter-dnssecOps.nameservers) ([#1](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/1)).
- In [dns-zz-consistency](#Test-Case-dns-zz-consistency), clarify that a secure delegation for the "nic" zone **MUST** be present in the TLD zone ([#16](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/16)).
- Update [`idn.testLabelsForOTE`](#idn.testLabelsForOTE) to v1.0.2 ([#17](https://github.com/icann/rst-test-specs/issues/17)).

name: v2025.01
body: This is the first stable release of the RST v2.0 test specifications.
